{"id": "aos002", "name": "Audio_Hospital_694_03_28", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, I'm coming in? Your classmates are here to visit you today too.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Aroma, are you feeling OK?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Sis Helena, here's the academic schedule for this month. Please show the lecture to her later.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "... How's she going to watch it when she's still in a coma?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Daniel！</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "She can, no need to worry. Her conditions are getting better by the day. Right now, she should be able to hear our conversation. Take a look at her right index finger. Can you hear us, Aroma?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Classmates"], "content": "..... Wow! It moved!\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma! It's me, Clara!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "It moved again! She really can hear you!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "See?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Tch... HEY! Aroma! If you can hear us, then get your lazy a** off the bed right now! How long do you plan to sleep like that, huh!?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Hey! Daniel!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Hmph. I'm going home.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel! Wait up!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "I'm sorry, sis Helena... He got chewed out by the lecturer at school today. He's not in a very good mood...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "It's fine... The hospital has scheduled an operation for her next month. They are going to use a new type of surgery to remove the debris pieces. After that, she will be able to go back to school and be with everyone again.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Really!? That's great news!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena... Ah! Iris, it's been a while. Are you here to visit Aroma?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Yes, I'm here to bring her the academic schedule. Ah, is there something important you want to discuss with sis Helena? It's about time I take my leave too. I will not disturb you guys.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No need to be so modest. Please come visit more often. Aroma will be very glad to see you. Oh right; about your two classmates, I just saw them run away in a hurry.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Those two... I'll go catch them. Thank you!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma、来たわよ。\n今日はお友達も来てくれたのよ。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Aroma…大丈夫？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Helenaさん、今月の授業のノートを持って来たんです。\nAromaに見せてあげて下さい。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……眠ってる人間にどうやってみせるんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Daniel！</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "気にしないで。\n最近は調子も良さそうなの。\n今、ここで話していることも聞こえているはずよ。\nほら、人差し指を見て。\nAroma。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["クラスメイトたち"], "content": "……動いた！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma！私よ！Claraよ！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "また動いた！聞こえてるんだ！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "でしょ？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "ッチ……おい！Aroma！このバカ！\n聞こえてるんなら早く目ぇ覚ませよ！\nいつまで寝てる気だよ！？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "ちょっと！Daniel！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "ふん、俺帰るわ。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel！待ってよ！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Helenaさん、ごめんなさい……\nDanielってば、今日アカデミーで叱られたから、気が立ってるんです……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "いいのよ……来月には新しい術式で頭の中の欠片を取り出すの。\nそしたら、またみんなとアカデミーに通えるわ。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "本当ですか！？やったぁ！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……あっ！Irisちゃん、久しぶりだね。\nAromaに会いに来てくれたのかい？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "はい。授業のノートを届けに。\nあ、何かお話があるんですよね？\nじゃあ、私は帰りますね。\nお邪魔になっちゃうと悪いし。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "いや、気にしなくていいんだよ。\nまた、会いにきてやってね。\nAromaも喜ぶから。\nそうだ！お友達2人がさっきバタバタ走って行ったよ。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "まったくもう……私追いかけますね！\nありがとうございました！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，我進來囉？今天妳同學也來看妳囉。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Aroma，還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Helena 姐，我帶了這個月的教學進度，請再放給她看吧。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "謝謝妳。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……她又還沒醒怎麼看？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Daniel！</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "可以喔，最近狀況越來越好了，我們現在講話她應該也是聽得到的，你們看她的右手食指。對嗎？Aroma。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學們"], "content": "……哇！動了！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma！我是 Clara！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "又動了！她聽得到妳耶！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "對吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "呿……喂！Aroma！妳這混蛋聽得到的話就趕快給我起床啊！到底要睡到什麼時候！？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "喂！Daniel！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "哼，我回去了。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel！等一下！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Helena 姐對不起喔……他今天在學院被講師修理了，心情不是很好……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "沒關係的……醫院下個月就要用新型的手術把碎片拿出來了，到時候她就能回去跟大家一起上課囉。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "真的嗎！？太好了！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……啊！Iris 好久不見，來看 Aroma 嗎？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "嗯，來拿教學進度給她。啊、你們要談事情嗎？我也差不多要走了，不打擾你們。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不會不會，有空常來，Aroma 會很開心的。對了，妳的兩個同學剛剛匆匆忙忙跑走了喔。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "真是的……我去追他們，謝謝！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma, 들어갈게? \n오늘은 친구들도 널 보러 왔더라.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Aroma, 괜찮은 거니?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Helena 언니, 이번 달 수업 진도 내용이에요. Aroma한테 꼭 보라고 전해주세요.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "응, 고맙구나.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……아직 깨어나지도 못했는데 그걸 어떻게 봐?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Daniel !!</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "요즘 상태가 조금씩 나아지고 있는 중이라서 괜찮단다. 우리가 지금 하는 말도 전부 들을 수 있고 말이야. 검지 손가락 잘 보렴. 그렇지, Aroma?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생들"], "content": "……와! 움직였다!\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma! 나야! Clara!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "또 움직였어! 정말로 들리나 봐!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "내 말 맞지?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "칫……야! Aroma 이 멍청아! 목소리가 들리면 냉큼 일어나라고! 대체 언제까지 자고 있을 거야!?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "야! Daniel!!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "흥! 먼저 갈래.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel ! 잠깐!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Helena 언니, 죄송해요.... 쟤 오늘 학교에서 강사님한테 혼났거든요... 그래서 기분이 많이 안 좋은 것 같은데...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "괜찮아…… 병원에서도 다음 달에 신기술로 파편 제거 수술을 할 예정이래. 수술받고 나면 아마 예전처럼 함께 수업할 수 있을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "정말이요!? 정말 잘 됐다!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……아! 오랜만이구나 Iris. Aroma를 보러 온 거니?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "네. 그리고 이번 달 수업 진도 내용도 전해줄 겸 왔어요. 두 분 말씀 나누세요. 방해되지 않도록 전 먼저 가보도록 하겠습니다.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아니야. 시간 나면 자주 와주렴. Aroma도 분명 기뻐할 테니깐. 아, 그런데  방금 다른 두 친구들은 엄청 다급하게 뛰어가고 있던데.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "어휴 정말이지…… 지금 따라가볼게요. 감사합니다!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，我進來囉？今天妳同學也來看妳囉。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Aroma，還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Helena 姐，我帶了這個月的教學進度，請再放給她看吧。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "謝謝妳。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……她又還沒醒怎麼看？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Daniel！</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "可以喔，最近狀況越來越好了，我們現在講話她應該也是聽得到的，你們看她的右手食指。對嗎？Aroma。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同學們"], "content": "……哇！動了！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma！我是 Clara！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "又動了！她聽得到妳耶！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "對吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "呿……喂！Aroma！妳這混蛋聽得到的話就趕快給我起床啊！到底要睡到什麼時候！？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "喂！Daniel！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "哼，我回去了。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Daniel！等一下！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Helena 姐對不起喔……他今天在學院被講師修理了，心情不是很好……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "沒關係的……醫院下個月就要用新型的手術把碎片拿出來了，到時候她就能回去跟大家一起上課囉。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "真的嗎！？太好了！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Helena……啊！Iris 好久不見，來看 Aroma 嗎？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "嗯，來拿教學進度給她。啊、你們要談事情嗎？我也差不多要走了，不打擾你們。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不會不會，有空常來，Aroma 會很開心的。對了，妳的兩個同學剛剛匆匆忙忙跑走了喔。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "真是的……我去追他們，謝謝！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_Hospital_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Hospital", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "Aroma，我进来啰？今天妳同学也来看妳啰。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "Aroma，还好吗？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Helena 姐，我带了这个月的教学进度，请再放给她看吧。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "谢谢妳。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……她又还没醒怎么看？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Daniel！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "可以喔，最近状况越来越好了，我们现在讲话她应该也是听得到的，你们看她的右手食指。对吗？ Aroma。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["同学们"], "content": "……哇！动了！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Aroma！我是 Clara！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Iris"], "content": "又动了！她听得到妳耶！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Helena"], "content": "对吧？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "呿……喂！ Aroma！妳这混蛋听得到的话就赶快给我起床啊！到底要睡到什么时候！ ？\n"}, {"i